<h1>@HI{{zehi}}</h1>

<h2> Formation </h2>

<ol>
<li> <strong>@HI{{zehi}}</strong>
</ol>

<h2> Definition </h2>

<p>
<strong>@HI{{zehi}}</strong> is usually used with expressions of hope or request. It emphasises
the meaning of these expressions.
</p>

<h2> Examples </h2>

<ol>
<li>
<table class="sentence">
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
      @HI{{<strong>zehi</strong>@KJ{{north^sea^road-way}}he @KJ{{going}}kitaidesu.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
      I want to go to Hokkaido very much.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
</ol>

